text:
I’ve been a fan of Martha’s for about seven years. She trained at the same school of human sexuality as I did. I know her knowledge of sexology topics is up to date and accurate. She has been a regular invited speaker to the Singapore Urological Association for several years. It’s been a joy to see her professional career blossom.
John Kamp, MD

Dr Martha Tara Lee is rare species, being the only Clinical Sexologist that I know in Singapore. She has great interpersonal skills and provides a safe and comfortable environment for her participants to contribute. I have been enjoying her Eros Coaching sessions and am amazed by the variety of subject matter and focus areas that Martha covers. Highly recommended for anyone wishing to walk on the wild side and at the same time being educated and entertained.

Dr Martha Tara Lee a very passionate and committed to her work and she will do what it takes to help her clients. She is very protective over her clients privacy and remain professional in her work. Being the pioneer in this industry, she has indeed set up a very high standard.

Dr Martha Lee is experienced, passionate and compassionate in her work. She is generous, hardworking and has impecable ethics. As an author of five books and pioneer in her industry, she is knowledgable and well-respected in her field of work.
Knowing Dr Martha since 2010. she is a professional and  passionate sexologist. Martha always put her client in her heart. I will never forget her helped in the past and her encouragement.
